# GG Krishi — Digital MRV WhatsApp Bot Implementation Plan

A WhatsApp-native **Digital MRV (Monitoring, Reporting, Verification)** infrastructure for decentralized biochar carbon credit verification, fraud detection, and farmer payout.

---

## System Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["👨‍🌾 Farmer (WhatsApp)"] -->|Messages / QR Scan| B["WhatsApp Business API<br/>(Gupshup / Twilio)"]
    B -->|Webhook POST| C["Node.js Backend<br/>(Express)"]
    C -->|Store| D["PostgreSQL Database"]
    C -->|Upload| E["AWS S3<br/>(Image Storage)"]
    C -->|Analyze| F["AI Vision Layer<br/>(OpenAI GPT-4o)"]
    C -->|Score| G["Fraud Engine"]
    C -->|Payout| H["UPI / Crypto<br/>(RazorpayX / Ethers.js)"]
    C -->|Anchor Hash| I["Polygon Blockchain<br/>(Optional)"]
    C -->|Serve| J["Operator Dashboard<br/>(React)"]
    F -->|Confidence Score| G
    G -->|Decision| D
```

---

