### 3. WhatsApp Business API Layer

#### [NEW] [src/whatsapp/webhook.ts](file:///Users/john/Desktop/projects/biochar/src/whatsapp/webhook.ts)

Handles incoming WhatsApp messages via POST webhook:

```
POST /api/whatsapp/webhook
```

**Message routing logic:**

| Message Pattern | Action |
|---|---|
| `"hi"` / `"start"` / first contact | → Onboarding flow |
| `GG-*` (bag ID pattern) | → Bag linking flow |
| Location message | → GPS capture for verification |
| Image message | → Image verification flow |
| `"status"` / `"reward"` | → Check verification / payment status |

#### [NEW] [src/whatsapp/sender.ts](file:///Users/john/Desktop/projects/biochar/src/whatsapp/sender.ts)

Sends templated replies, buttons, and interactive messages back to farmers.

#### [NEW] [src/whatsapp/flows.ts](file:///Users/john/Desktop/projects/biochar/src/whatsapp/flows.ts)

WhatsApp Flows (mini-app UI) for structured data collection during onboarding.

