## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

Run all tests with:
```bash
cd /Users/john/Desktop/projects/biochar && npm test
```

| Test File | What It Covers |
|---|---|
| `src/fraud/__tests__/scoring.test.ts` | Composite fraud score calculation with various risk combinations |
| `src/fraud/__tests__/imageHasher.test.ts` | SHA-256 and pHash duplicate detection |
| `src/fraud/__tests__/gpsValidator.test.ts` | Haversine boundary check, accuracy rejection |
| `src/ai/__tests__/visionVerifier.test.ts` | AI response parsing, confidence threshold logic |
| `src/flows/__tests__/bagLinking.test.ts` | Bag claim lifecycle, duplicate rejection |
| `src/flows/__tests__/verification.test.ts` | End-to-end verification flow logic |

### Manual Verification

1. **WhatsApp Flow Test:** Send messages to the WhatsApp Business number and verify the full flow: onboarding → bag scan → location → photo → AI check → payout notification
2. **Fraud Simulation:** Submit a second scan of an already-claimed bag → expect rejection message
3. **Dashboard Review:** Open operator dashboard and verify verification records appear with correct status, fraud score, and image preview
